  //ALEX

  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.1": "Hey, hey, hey...$l$b$@, I'm an athlete. I've got above-average physical stamina.$s#$b$But you're testing my limits in a way I never trained for.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.2": "@... you know I'm not one to embarrass easily, right?$l$b$Yeah. But I just saw someone give us a look I'm never gonna forget.$s#$b$Thanks for that.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.3": "Okay, okay, pause.$l$b$I know I'm hard to resist, but you're overdoing it in a way that even leaves ME speechless.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.4": "@, on the field I know exactly what to do under pressure.$l$b$But out here in public? You leave me with no playbook.$l#$b$And that doesn't happen to me with many people, so keep this secret.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.5": "Okay, I know I'm irresistible. That's a fact.$l$b$But you could at least wait until we're alone to act like this.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.6": "Fine, I admit it.$l$b$I thought I was the one who impressed people... but then you flipped the script here and now I don't even remember where I was headed.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.7": "@...$l$b$I train every morning. Lift weights. Run. Prepare for anything.$l#$b$Except this time I didn't prepare for you, and that's pretty unfair.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.8": "Whoa, hold on! I-if my grandpa sees us hugging like this, he's gonna grumble about it all day!$l#$b#Give me a break, I've got nowhere to hide out here.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.9": "H-hey ${champ^champ}$, I like attention, everyone knows that.$l$b$But this kind of attention... is pretty different.$l#$b$And this kind of attention... I'd rather have it when we're alone somewhere more private.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.10": "@... I train every day to have mental control.$l$b$Focus. Discipline. A cool head.$s#$b$...But then you come along and undo all of it in public, and you still find it funny. Unbelievable.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.11": "@! Hey, hey — people are watching!$l$b$Not that I care, because I don't.$s#$b$...But people are watching.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.12": "Okay, look...$l$b$I like you. A lot. That's already clear.$l#$b$But you could at least give me a heads-up before ambushing me in the middle of town like that.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Alex.13": "H-hey, @, stop.$l$b$If my grandma hears about what's happening here, she'll never let me hear the end of it.$s#$b$And anyone around here could tell her.$l",

  "IndoorKisses.Alex.1": "Are you ${crazy^crazy}$, doing this with so many people sharing the same roof as us?$l#$b#My face is on fire, play it cool before someone asks if I'm feeling sick!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.2": "Hold on, ${champ^champ}$! You realize people are watching, right?$l$b$Not that I care. They can watch all they want.$h#$b$...$s#$b$Okay, I care a little. Just a little.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.3": "(Whispering) @, come on! I've got a reputation to maintain...$l#$b#How am I supposed to look now with you turning me red in front of everyone?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.4": "Whoa, hold on!$l#$b#If anyone else sees us like this, we're gonna be the main topic of the whole town...$s#$b#Save all that energy for later, please.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.5": "We're not alone in here, @! Everyone inside is watching us.$l#$b#I like being the center of attention, but not like this! My face is burning.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.6": "I swear people here already stopped paying attention to anything else just to stare at us.$s#$b#You're wrecking my composure, give me a second to breathe...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.7": "Hey hey! Pinning me down and attacking me with kisses in here isn't fair, that's a cheap shot!$l#$b#We're not alone in here, give me some room to breathe...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.8": "My heart's beating faster than when I do my push-up sets!$s#$b#S-stop it, you're leaving me with nowhere to hide my face.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.9": "Whoa... I think the air in here just got super stuffy... or is it just me?$l#$b#You're driving me crazy kissing me like this, let go of me a little!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.10": "@, I'm an athletic guy, but I don't have the physical conditioning to handle you kissing me nonstop in here in front of everyone!$s#$b#Save that for when we're in the bedroom...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.11": "I always knew I was a great trophy, but you don't have to show me off to everyone in here!$l#$b#My face is on fire, seriously...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.12": "(Whispering) S-stop it... I know you love me, but save some of that enthusiasm for somewhere private.$l#$b#Someone's gonna come get our attention any minute now...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Alex.13": "Whoa, you've got energy to spare today, huh?$l#$b#But the walls in here have ears... and eyes!$s#$b#Let's hold back a bit before we become the talk of the town.$l",

  //ELLIOTT

  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.1": "My sweet inspiration...$l#$b#If you keep kissing me with such fervor, I fear I shall swoon like the hero of an old romance novel.$s#$b#Shall we have a shred of mercy for our audience, hmm?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.2": "By the seas, @!$l#$b#Your display of affection is worthy of an epic poem, but... $s#$b#...perhaps we ought to save some of that poetry for when we're alone?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.3": "Oh! @...$l#$b#Are you trying to leave me utterly speechless in the middle of the street?$s#$b#Because it's working remarkably well... I've even forgotten where I was headed.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.4": "Ah, you know... I've written about love without restraint, about stolen kisses in public places...$s$b$I thought it was romantic.$s#$b$But now that I find myself the protagonist, I must reconsider my position.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.5": "P-please stop, @.$l$b$I've written about love with a precision I take pride in.$s#$b$But I've never written about having such a hot face in a public place where anyone could appear at any moment.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.6": "A single kiss from you is pure poetry... but this many kisses, in public?$l#$b#That's an entire anthology of scandalous romance, @!$s#$b#And I am literally running out of breath.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.7": "Oh, ${my dear^my dear}$ @...$l#$b#Do you wish to make such an ardent declaration right here, in full view of everyone?$l#$b#I fear the villagers are not prepared for such passion!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.8": "You are like a storm of affection!$l#$b#I surrender completely to your charms, but... $s#$b#...if we don't stop, we'll soon be the main scandal at the Saloon!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.9": "Wait, wait.$l$b$In my mind I always kept my composure in situations like this.$s#$b$In practice, in a public place where anyone might pass by... it's not quite the same.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.10": "Ah, the sweet and intoxicating taste of your kisses...$l#$b#But @, if you keep seducing me like this in a public place...$s#$b#How do you expect me to face polite society afterward?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.11": "My wonderful flower...$l#$b#I adore your boldness, but my heartbeat has become dangerously accelerated.$s#$b#...Spare this poor writer, won't you?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.12": "I always dreamed of a passionate romance, but you exceed all my expectations, @.$l#$b#Just... please... $s#$b#Give me a moment to breathe before I collapse from so much love in the middle of the street.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Elliott.13": "I'm quite certain my face is conveying things I would never say aloud.$l$b$And everyone around us can see it.$s#$b$And there is absolutely nothing I can do about it.$l",

  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.1": "Ah, @... the fervor of our passion is beautiful, but I beg that we mind our manners!$s#$b#We have an entire audience right here inside, and I feel my nerves on edge...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.2": "I-I feel as though we're starring in our very own romantic stage play...$l#$b#The only trouble is I was absolutely not prepared to handle such a close audience today!$s#$b#Release me a little, won't you?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.3": "E-wait...$l#$b#An overwhelming romance is any writer's dream, but being the main spectacle in here is a bit much for my poor heart.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.4": "By the heavens, my face is burning with embarrassment...$l#$b#Please, pull back a little... there isn't enough room in here to hide from these prying eyes...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.5": "If we continue with this abundance of kisses, I fear someone will call us out for our lack of composure!$s#$b#That would be a terrible blow to my dignity.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.6": "O-look, @... I would love to recite poetry about the taste of your lips, but with all these ears so close by, I feel my cheeks burning like embers!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.7": "(Whispering) E-wait...$l#$b#If we had a bit more privacy, I would surrender to this completely...$l#$b#But in here? I feel we're committing a scandal worthy of a cheap serial novel!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.8": "With every kiss of yours, I feel as though I'm floating in a sea of emotions...$l#$b#But please, bring me back down to earth before we bump into something and draw even more attention.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.9": "My dear, your passion is like a summer storm, but this room is far too cramped for such a gale!$s#$b#Give me a moment to catch my breath and regain my composure.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.10": "I write about torrid love affairs often, but experiencing one with people watching so closely is terribly embarrassing!$l#$b#Look at me, I must be the color of a crab!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.11": "A true gentleman knows when to withdraw, and with so many witnesses around us, I feel that moment has arrived.$s#$b#Save this ardor for when we're alone...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.12": "You leave me utterly intoxicated, @...$l#$b#But I implore you, pause for a moment. I cannot even form a sentence with all these eyes upon us.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Elliott.13": "(Whispering) My sweet inspiration, I beg you... you're ruffling my hair and I feel that everyone in here is staring at us!$l",

  //HARVEY

  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.1": "I know I'm a doctor, but I swear I don't know how to cure what you do to me.$l#$b#My knees are weak and my head is spinning.$s#$b#Please, @, have mercy on my heart.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.2": "@... w-wait a moment!$s#$b#I'm the local doctor, people trust my professional composure.$l#$b#How am I supposed to examine anyone later with my face completely on fire?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.3": "Oh goodness...$l#$b#From a medical standpoint, the benefits of endorphin release are undeniable...$s#$b#But from a social standpoint, I'm about to faint from sheer embarrassment!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.4": "@, I truly appreciate your affection, I really do...$l#$b#But if you keep kissing me like this in public, I'm going to have a vasovagal episode!$s#$b#...I mean, I'm going to end up fainting right here.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.5": "*Pant... pant...*$s#$b#@, I think I'm hyperventilating.$l#$b#Wouldn't you rather save some of this intensive treatment for when we're at the clinic? Behind the curtains?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.6": "@, please...$l#$b#I'm not young enough to handle such strong emotions in front of everyone!$s#$b#Give your favorite doctor a break... my face can't take any more blushing.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.7": "My body temperature is rising far too quickly...$l#$b#I must have a fever! No, wait, it's just you kissing me nonstop in the middle of the street.$s#$b#This is too much exposure for my emotional health.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.8": "What will Maru think if she sees me like this?!$s#$b#Or worse, the whole town!$l#$b#@, have mercy on my clinical reputation... and my sanity too.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.9": "Um, @... I think I just saw Mayor Lewis looking this way.$s#$b#M-my face is burning so much I'm going to need an urgent cold compress.$l#$b#Are you trying to kill me with embarrassment?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.10": "*Sigh*... you're really not going to stop doing this, are you?$l#$b#Fine, you win. But if I need oxygen after this...$s#$b#The medical responsibility is entirely yours.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.11": "B-but @, what about germs?!$s#$b#I mean... I love your kisses, but this repeated exposure in a public, unsterilized environment...$l#$b#Ah, who am I kidding, I just don't know where to hide my face!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.12": "H-hey, @... my heart rate just spiked to 120 beats per minute!$s#$b#That's not safe for my blood pressure in the middle of the street.$l#$b#Can we take a small clinical break?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Harvey.13": "H-help... I no longer know how to behave in society.$s#$b#@, if I don't survive this fulminant attack of public affection...$l#$b#Know that I loved every second of it. B-but that's enough for now!$l",

  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.1": "Oh, goodness... @! My heart rate just spiked.$s#$b#We're in an enclosed space with people nearby, and this is not professional at all!$s#$b#C-control yourself a little, will you?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.2": "(Whispering) Please, we need to stop!$l#$b#If anyone else sees me in this state, I'll lose all credibility as a doctor.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.3": "M-my blood pressure must be through the roof right now.$l#$b#You're leaving me short of breath, and this stuffy room isn't helping!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.4": "I think my glasses are even fogging up from all this heat.$l#$b#You leave me utterly intoxicated, but being the center of attention in here is dreadful!$s#$b#Let's save all this intimacy for later, okay?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.5": "You... you're giving me severe tachycardia!$l#$b#And with these people so close by, my social stress level is also hitting its limit!$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.6": "By the heavens, my body temperature is rising drastically.$l#$b#Do you want me to faint right here in front of everyone?$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.7": "Wait, @! There are too many people in this room, I was definitely not trained to handle such high levels of social exposure.$s#$b#Oh goodness, my face is burning up...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.8": "C-control yourself, please! There are people in here watching us!$s#$b#Oh goodness, my face must be redder than the apples on your farm...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.9": "(Whispering) @, I beg you to stop! As a health professional, I recommend immediate distancing!$s#$b#A-at least until we're alone...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.10": "I-I think I need a glass of water... and a little personal space.$s#$b#People are watching us in here, @. What will they think of the two of us?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.11": "(Whispering) I-I just heard someone clear their throat right behind us!$s#$b#I think they've already noticed what we're doing, and I don't know where to hide my face...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.12": "My legs feel weak... and there's nowhere to hide in here!$s#$b#If we keep this up, I myself am going to need medical attention very soon!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Harvey.13": "I-I can't afford to be caught in such an... intimate moment in front of others.$s#$b#Please, ${my love^my dear}$, have mercy on my reputation and my health!$l",

  //SAM

  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.1": "H-hey, @... haha...$l#$b#I know I'm irresistible and all, but we're in the middle of the street!$s#$b#My face is on fire, you know that?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.2": "Whoa, @!$l#$b#If Sebastian or Abigail see us making out like this, they'll never let me live it down!$s#$b#Give me a break to breathe, would you?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.3": "Hey, slow down...$l#$b#Not that I'm complaining, far from it, but we're like, in a public place.$s#$b#Let's save this for when we have a bit more privacy?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.4": "W-wait a sec!$l#$b#Imagine if Vincent runs by here and sees this?!$s#$b#He'll go tell my mom, and she'll scold me even though I'm already an adult!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.5": "Hehe... you're kinda addicted to me, huh?$l#$b#I really love that, seriously...$l#$b#But if you don't stop, I think I'm gonna explode from embarrassment!$l0",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.6": "Wait, wait, wait!$l#$b#You're gonna mess up my hair like this! It took me forever to get it looking like this today.$l#$b#...And I'm also running out of breath.$l0",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.7": "H-holy cow, @...$l#$b#My heart's beating faster than a drum solo.$l#$b#If anyone's watching, I'm gonna wanna dig a hole and hide!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.8": "Alright, alright, you win the kissing championship!$l#$b#Now let me recover my HP, please?$l#$b#I don't even know where I was headed anymore...$l0",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.9": "I think my face is the same color as my hair right now...$s#$b#@, I love you, but the whole town doesn't need a live show from us, right?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.10": "Hey, if you kiss me again, I think I'm gonna end up tripping over my own feet!$l#$b#I'm not that well-coordinated when I'm dying of embarrassment, you know?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.11": "Okay, I give up! I can't act natural with you attacking me with kisses like this!$l#$b#I'm gonna have to lock myself in my room and play video games until this redness fades from my face.$l0",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.12": "If you keep making me this flustered...$l#$b#I swear I'm gonna forget how to play the chords to my own song!$s#$b#Have mercy on me, come on?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sam.13": "Hey, @, hold up, haha. $l0#$b#If my mom walks by and sees us hugging like this, I'm gonna hear her teasing and giggling about it all day.$l",

  "IndoorKisses.Sam.1": "Man, I swear I'm melting! Not even when I mess up a skateboard trick do I get this red.$l#$b#Give me a break, the people in here are watching us.$l0",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.2": "Wait, wait, wait! The air in here ran out after that.$l#$b#Everyone's noticing what's going on, we gotta play it cool!$s#$b#Look at the ceiling or the wall or something!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.3": "(Whispering) Whoa, @, we're sharing the same roof with all these people!$l#$b#My face must look like a bell pepper, give me a break!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.4": "Whoa, hold on! You trying to put on a show for everyone in here?$l0#$b#Because I'm not ready for that! Seriously, I'm dying of embarrassment...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.5": "Whoa...$l#$b#My hands are sweating so much I couldn't even hold a guitar pick right now.$l#$b#Play it cool, people here are watching us!$l8#$b#Pretend nothing happened.$l0",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.6": "W-wait, if I bump into something and drop it, it's totally your fault!$l#$b#You're making me dizzy and there's nowhere to run in here!$l#$b#I'm gonna end up tripping over my own feet like this...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.7": "I actually love this way too much, but... with all these people around?$l#$b#I'm gonna end up evaporating from the heat if you don't give me some room.$l0",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.8": "(Whispering) Man, Seb or Abigail are gonna tease me for the rest of my life.$s#$b#Hold up, the space in here is already tight enough!$l0#$b#...I promise I'll make it up to you when we're alone...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.9": "H-holy cow, did someone turn on the heater in here or am I just melting from nerves?$l0#$b#...You leave me completely speechless, @.$l#$b#Let's stop, or I swear I'm gonna faint from the heat.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.10": "Whoa... we don't even have anywhere to run if someone comes to talk to us right now.$l#$b#Give me a break, I'm breaking out in a cold sweat!$l#$b#M-my heart's racing a mile a minute, help.$l0",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.11": "S-seriously, @, we're drawing a lot of attention...$l#$b#I'm dying of embarrassment, there's nowhere for me to look to escape this situation.$l#$b#Let's ease up on this a bit before someone comes over to talk to us.$l0",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.12": "I swear if Vincent shows up in here out of nowhere, I'll drop dead from embarrassment.$l#$b#How about we save this for when we're alone in some dark, private corner?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sam.13": "You're too much, @, and I love it... b-but I'm not the most discreet guy in the world when it comes to handling this with so many people watching.$l#$b#My face is on fire and I've got nowhere to hide it in here...$l",

  //SEBASTIAN

  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.1": "E-hey... wait...$l#$b#@, are you really ${determined^determined}$ to ruin what's left of my dignity right here in public?$l#$b#People are watching... and I can already feel my face heating up.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.2": "S-seriously, @? You're gonna keep doing this here?$l#$b#I can barely leave the house without feeling judged, and now this... in front of the whole town?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.3": "Hey, @, you do realize we're not alone here, right? Because I sure do.$s#$b#A little more of this and I'll turn red enough to compete with the tomatoes you grow.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.4": "L-look, I genuinely like it when you're ${affectionate^affectionate}$ with me...$s#$b#But out here it's too much for me. My social battery just hit zero from this scene alone.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.5": "@... do you have any idea how many people have already looked at us since this started?$l#$b#Because I do.$s#$b#A little more and I'm going to evaporate from embarrassment right here.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.6": "Wait a second! Did you freeze or something?$l#$b#I thought my code was the buggy one, but you're kind of repeating the same action over and over!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.7": "Okay, hold on a second...$l#$b#I need to compose myself before someone starts clapping or making fun of my face.$s#$b#You really love seeing me flustered, don't you?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.8": "@, if you keep kissing me like this in public, I'm gonna explode from embarrassment.$l#$b#So... please... take it easy, before I melt right here.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.9": "Uh, @, I know you're being ${affectionate^affectionate}$... but...$l#$b#This is public, not a private place... if we keep this up, we're gonna be the main topic of the whole town.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.10": "T-take it easy, @...$l#$b#I'm already not a fan of being in public, you don't need to make it worse by exposing me like this...$s#$b#Let's go somewhere darker, please.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.11": "Uh... I like this, okay?$l#$b#It's just that maybe... maybe you could not do it this many times in a row right here?$s#$b#My face is already burning and I still need to exist in society afterward.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.12": "Look, even the frogs down at the lake have more privacy than we do right now.$l#$b#You're driving me crazy... in a very embarrassing way.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Sebastian.13": "Hey hey, take it easy...$l#$b#You can't just keep kissing me like this in public and expect me to keep acting normal.$l#$b#I'm already running out of places to hide my face.$s",

  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.1": "Ugh, I should've brought one of my comic books so I could cover my face.$s#$b#Y-you just grab me out of nowhere in front of everyone and expect me to be fine?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.2": "S-seriously, I go out a little to try and be more sociable, and you put me through this?$s#$b#I don't know how to deal with an audience, you know that very well, and people are staring...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.3": "Hey hey, take it easy... my social battery was already super low, and with you exposing me like this, it just hit zero.$l#$b#People are staring at us...$s#$b#Let's stop this before I evaporate from embarrassment.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.4": "E-hey! If you don't stop right now, I swear I'll run out of here.$s#$b#Seriously, we're in an enclosed space full of people, and I hate attention.$s#$b#...Can we continue later, just somewhere darker... okay?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.5": "(Whispering) Wait! If Sam or Abigail see us hugging here, my peace and quiet is over.$l#$b#They'll never let me hear the end of it during all our tabletop RPG sessions!$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.6": "Uhh... I-I think my brain froze up with all this sudden kissing.$l#$b#The worst part is there's nowhere for me to hide in here...$s#$b#Everyone's watching, @, go easy on me.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.7": "@, w-wait!$l#$b#People in here won't stop looking this way, and I don't know where to hide...$l#$b#Let go of me before my face explodes from embarrassment, I'm serious.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.8": "I love you, truly, but these public kisses of yours are dangerous.$l#$b#I don't know where to hide my face, I feel like the walls are closing in with so many people around.$s#$b#Let go of me, @... I promise I'll make it up to you later.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.9": "@... I already don't feel very comfortable around a lot of people, and you hugging me like this only makes it worse.$l#$b#My hands are cold and sweaty from all this nervousness with everyone staring.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.10": "I thought the monsters in the mines were scary, but this exposure is a thousand times worse.#$b#Hold up, @... my face is stinging.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.11": "I-I swear I'm going to start wearing my hood up all the time if you keep doing this.$l#$b#Every sound echoes in here, everyone's seeing and hearing us.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.12": "Hold on! My mom could see us!$l#$b#And I'll never have any peace if she catches me like this...$s#$b#I was definitely not built for this level of exposure.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Sebastian.13": "E-hey, take it easy!$l#$b#We're sharing the same roof with other people, @, we can't just be hugging like this.$s#$b#My face must be the color of my mom's paint... l-let me breathe a little.$l",

  //SHANE

  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.1": "Ugh... @, what's gotten into you today?$s#$b#We're literally in the middle of the street. M-my face is on fire, stop it.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.2": "Seriously? Right here in front of everyone?$l#$b#If you keep being this ${clingy^clingy}$ with me, I swear I'll lock myself in the coop and never come out.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.3": "S-stop it, @!$l#$b#I'm not used to this much attention, let alone in public.$s#$b#...Not that I want you to stop forever. Just... not here.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.4": "Look, I actually like a bit of affection when it's just us...$s#$b#But out here? I just want to bury my head in a hole from embarrassment.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.5": "Man... have you completely lost it?$s#$b#We're in the middle of the street and I hate being the center of attention!$l#$b#Save all this clinginess for when we're somewhere private...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.6": "I need a sip of ice-cold Joja Cola after this...$l#$b#My blood pressure must be through the roof with all this exposure.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.7": "You want to finish off what little dignity I have left, is that it?$l#$b#'Cause if so, you're doing a great job kissing me in front of the whole town.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.8": "Charlie behaves better in public than you, you know?$l#$b#Can you hold back a little before I fall apart right here?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.9": "Okay, okay, I get it, you love me. The whole world got the message too.$l#$b#Now please, let's get out of here before I evaporate from embarrassment.$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.10": "W-wait... this is a bit embarrassing, @...$s#$b#I'm gonna start charging you a fee for every public kiss if you don't stop this right now.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.11": "Take it easy there, tick...$l#$b#I'm not made of iron to handle this much clinginess without getting embarrassed. People are watching!$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.12": "If Marnie sees us hugging like this, I'll never have peace again.$l#$b#She'll be asking embarrassing questions for the rest of the year!$s#$b#S-so, please, let go of me a little.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Shane.13": "L-look, I actually like it when you get this ${clingy^clingy}$, but...$l#$b#My face looks like a bell pepper it's so hot. Can you stop kissing me in front of the whole town?$s",

  "IndoorKisses.Shane.1": "Have you completely lost your mind? They're watching us in here!$l#$b#If Marnie sees this, I'll never have a moment's peace again.$s#$b#Let go of me before I become the joke of the whole town...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.2": "@, seriously... c-can you save this level of affection for when we're alone?$l#$b#My face is on fire, and I promise it's not because of hot peppers...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.3": "(Whispering) You know, you could just as easily kiss me in a corner where no one's watching, right?$l#$b#Hugging me with an audience here definitely isn't my style.$s#$b#Seriously, I'm breaking out in a cold sweat with all these stares...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.4": "Even Charlie has more sense of personal space than you when you decide to get this clingy!$l#$b#There are people right next to us watching, @. And I don't know how to handle this!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.5": "Hey hey, take it easy!$l#$b#If Jas shows up out of nowhere and sees us hugging, what am I gonna tell her?#$b#I don't have the mental capacity to explain this stuff to a kid!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.6": "I spend most of my life trying to go unnoticed by others...#$b#And then you come along and turn me into the center of everyone's attention.$l#$b#I swear I'm gonna end up digging a hole in the ground here.$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.7": "Man, my heart's racing... and I swear it's not from too much coffee today.$l#$b#Everyone can see and hear us.$s#$b#Give me a break before I have an embarrassment attack in front of them.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.8": "You seriously chose this exact spot to do this?$l#$b#I hate being stared at, @, you know that very well.$s#$b#Save it for later, I feel like a cornered clown right now...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.9": "S-stop it, my face is redder than pizza sauce...$l#$b#Seriously, my shoulders are tense and I don't even know where to look without meeting someone's eyes in here.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.10": "(Whispering) @, what are you doing?!? Everyone's watching us!$l#$b#And people aren't used to seeing me... like this... it's drawing way too much attention.$s#$b#...Let go of me, I promise I'll make it up to you later.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.11": "Look... I really do like this, okay?$l#$b#But this place is way too stuffy for you to be smothering me with kisses out of nowhere!$s#$b#I'm melting from heat and embarrassment... I need to breathe...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.12": "H-hey, @, I don't think this is a good place for this... especially with everyone sharing the same space and watching us!$l#$b#My reputation's going down the drain, I don't know where to hide my face.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Shane.13": "You're unbearable when you decide to get needy around a bunch of people, you know that?$s#$b#But the worst part is I can't push you away.$l#$b#...At least try to control yourself a little until we're alone...$l",

  //ABIGAIL

  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.1": "Hehe, you're a pretty hard ${guy^girl}$ to keep in check, huh?$l#$b#But seriously, let go of me a little, I need to breathe.$h",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.2": "I-if you don't stop this right now, I'm gonna have to pull out my sword!$h#$b#...Just kidding, but seriously, @! We're in a public place!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.3": "W-wait, @! You know I don't really care what others think...$l#$b#But kissing me nonstop right here in the middle of the street is a bit much, don't you think?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.4": "Haha, okay, okay, that's enough!$l#$b#If you wanna kiss me this badly, we could at least go to the cemetery or the lake.$l#$b#There aren't as many gossipy people to spy on us there.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.5": "H-hey, @, what's gotten into you?!$l#$b#We're in the middle of the street! My face must look like a fire quartz right now...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.6": "Whoa, @...$l#$b#If this were a video game, my energy bar would've already hit zero from embarrassment.$l#$b#Seriously, @, let's take a break to breathe a little.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.7": "Whoa, hold on!$l#$b#Did you decide to test how embarrassed you can make me in public?$l#$b#I love this, but I think it's better if we do this somewhere darker and more private.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.8": "W-wait a moment...$l#$b#I love being with you, but the people in town are super gossipy.$s#$b#Can we be a little more discreet?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.9": "Look... it's not that I'm not enjoying this...$s#$b#But could we, I don't know, do this somewhere more private before the whole town starts applauding?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.10": "Okay, you win.$l#$b#I'm officially flustered. Can we stop putting on a show for the whole town now?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.11": "W-wait! Look over there, a bat!$l#$b#...Didn't work, huh? It's just that I don't know how to react when you get this ${clingy^clingy}$ in public...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.12": "Hey, @... I think we should take a break, haha.$l#$b#I know we're enjoying this, but we're in a public place, and people are gonna start staring.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Abigail.13": "You really like teasing me, don't you?$l#$b#I'm nearly hiding inside my coat from embarrassment.$s#$b#Save some of these kisses for when we go explore the mines, how about that?$l",

  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.1": "Hey, hold on! My mom has a radar for this kind of thing, you know?$l#$b#If she shows up and sees us hugging, the lecture's gonna last a whole month.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.2": "Man, not even when I'm cornered by the Prairie King boss do I feel this trapped!$h#$b#We're in a place full of people and you attack me with kisses out of nowhere?$l#$b#My face is on fire!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.3": "E-hey! I might be tough down in the mines, but dealing with all these stares is complicated.$l#$b#My sword's no use defending me from this embarrassment you're putting me through! I don't even know where to hide my face...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.4": "(Whispering) You know I love breaking the rules, but a public display in here is too much!$h#$b#People already think I'm weird, no need to give them more reason to stare.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.5": "The air in here is already stuffy, and with you hugging me like this I'm about to melt.$l#$b#Everyone's watching, @, and the worst part is there's no window for me to escape through!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.6": "Hold on! If my dad walks by and starts grumbling about 'appropriate behavior,' it's your fault.$h#$b#I can't stand his lectures anymore, so please play it cool!$s#$b#Seriously, my cheeks are apple-red right now...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.7": "@! You're wrecking all my composure in front of these people!$s#$b#How am I supposed to function in society if you leave me all melted and blushing?$l#$b#Give me a second to breathe, the walls have eyes in here.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.8": "Seriously, my social HP is completely drained from you smothering me with kisses out of nowhere.$l#$b#These people are staring at us like we're the final boss of their game.#$b#Pause the romance right there, we'll continue this level in the bedroom.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.9": "(Whispering) Man, if I'd known you were gonna do this, I would've brought my sword to fend you off!$h#$b#Kidding, I wouldn't do that, but seriously, I'm freaking out with all these people whispering around us.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.10": "(Whispering) Y-you're really clueless, you know that?$h#$b#We're sharing oxygen with other people in here!$l#$b#My heart's beating so fast I think it's gonna jump out of my chest any second.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.11": "Hey hey, take it easy!$l#$b#People won't take their eyes off us, and you don't even seem to care!$h#$b#Save all these kisses for when there's no audience around, please.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.12": "L-listen... I love that you're this ${clingy^clingy}$, but in an enclosed space like this it's just mean!$h#$b#My brain stopped working and I feel everyone judging us from here.#$b#I'm gonna explode from embarrassment.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Abigail.13": "Hey! If you think you're gonna beat me by ambushing me in an enclosed space...$h#$b#You're right.$l#$b#I have absolutely no strategy for dealing with affection in public...$l#$b#But I'm begging you, let's save this for when we're alone, okay?$l",

  //EMILY

  "OutdoorKisses.Emily.1": "Whoa, @! My aura is vibrating in such a strong, bright shade of pink right now that I think the whole town can see it!$l#$b#I-I need a moment to harmonize all this energy.$l",
