  "OutdoorKisses.Emily.10": "W-wait! I need to do a quick meditation dance to calm my heart.$l#$b#You have no idea how flustered you make me when you do this in public.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Emily.11": "The energy of love you're radiating is beautiful, but it's drawing everyone's stares!$s#$b#Shall we save this moment for later? I promise I'll make it up to you.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Emily.12": "Wow! I feel like I just woke up from a beautiful, crazy dream!$l#$b#You take me out of orbit, but my shyness is begging you to stop for a second.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Emily.13": "Your vibrational frequency is wonderful today, @...$l#$b#B-but my face is so hot you could fry an egg on it! Give me a break.$l",

  "IndoorKisses.Emily.1": "Oh, @...$l#$b#Our energy is so strong, but everyone in here is watching!$l#$b#My chakras just took a leap with all this sudden kissing.$l#$b#My aura must be glowing a deep pink from embarrassment...$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.2": "I love spreading love, but you raised the vibrations in here way too much!$l#$b#I feel everyone's stares crossing our energy right now.$s#$b#Let's breathe a little, my heart's racing.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.3": "(Whispering) W-wait a minute!$l#$b#The energy in here got so dense I can barely think.$l#$b#Give me a second to hide this hot face...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.4": "Wow... even my crystals must be pretty warm with all our energy!$l#$b#I love your affection, but people weren't ready to feel all this vibration from us.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.5": "@... you just made my aura spin, you know that?$l#$b#But in a place like this, this much affection draws a lot of attention.$s#$b#My cheeks are on fire, let's play it cool...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.6": "W-wait, @...$l#$b#I love our connection, but sharing it with this many people is suffocating.$s#$b#...Shall we channel this energy for when we're alone?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.7": "Wow, @, you changed the vibration of this whole room out of nowhere!$l#$b#I'm dizzy and people won't stop looking at the two of us.$l#$b#Let go of me just a little, I'm completely losing my composure.$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.8": "I-I'm getting dizzy, let go of me just a bit...$s#$b#@, having so many people watch this is making me really embarrassed.$l#$b#I don't even remember what I was going to do...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.9": "@, control yourself a little!$l#$b#In an enclosed space with everyone watching, the energy gets way too intense.$l#$b#Let's breathe a bit, I wasn't ready for this alignment.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.10": "A-ah, wait!$l#$b#Seeing people watch us kiss like this sent my energy flying in every direction.$l#$b#I-I need to breathe a little, just a little...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Emily.11": "(Whispering) I-I love expressing my feelings, but everyone in here is watching us.$s#$b#My temperature rose in a way not even tea could fix.$s#$b#...Save this energy for later, when we're alone.$l",
