  "IndoorKisses.Emily.13": "Oh, @, my heart is beating at a vibration I didn't even know existed.$l#$b#I don't mind being authentic, but doing this in here is a lot of pressure.$s#$b#Give me a moment to calm down...$l",

  //HALEY

  "OutdoorKisses.Haley.1": "Ugh, @, stop! You're gonna ruin my brand new lipstick!$s#$b#And besides, we're in the middle of the street, everyone's watching!$l",
