  "OutdoorKisses.Haley.8": "I swear I'm gonna start charging you an expensive bottle of perfume for every kiss you give me in public.$l#$b#You're making me dizzy and I hate losing my composure!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Haley.9": "Oh my god, what will people think?!$s#$b#You can't just attack me with kisses in the middle of the street like I'm some kind of trophy!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Haley.10": "Y-you're making me really hot and I'm gonna start sweating!$s#$b#I just got out of the shower and something like this would be a social disaster, @, so please, stop for a bit!$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Haley.11": "I love affection, truly...$l#$b#But out here? Everyone's gonna gossip and I'll become the talk of the whole town!$l",
