  "IndoorKisses.Haley.1": "Hey, wait... even my perfume must've evaporated with all this heat.$l#$b#And with everyone watching, the situation gets a thousand times worse.$l#$b#Save this romance for later, I'm dying of embarrassment!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.2": "Do you think I spend hours getting ready just for you to mess me up in front of everyone?$a#$b#Play it cool, I can feel everyone's stares in here.$s#$b#Ugh, my face must be all red.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.3": "(Whispering) @, control yourself!$l#$b#We're not in our own living room, and there are people watching us!$s#$b#Stop kissing me like this, I'm burning up from embarrassment.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.4": "Ew, it's way too stuffy in here for you to be this ${clingy^clingy}$.#$b#And the worst part is the whole town's watching us.$s#$b#Give me some space, I need to fix my hair!$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.5": "I love it when you give me attention, but does it have to be in here? I don't want to be tomorrow's gossip.$s#$b#I'll let you keep going... just somewhere more private.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.6": "Wow, you totally messed me up! My hair's a mess.$s#$b#...And people are staring at us.$l#$b#Save these kisses for when we have more privacy.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.7": "Ugh, stop it for a bit! Have you lost your mind?$s#$b#People here have nothing better to do than stare this way!$s#$b#...Let go of me, I need to check my lipstick...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.8": "Y-you trying to give me a heart attack, or what?$l$l#$b#I just touched up my makeup and you're making me all sweaty from nerves!$l#$b#Seriously, look around, everyone stopped to watch the show.$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.9": "H-hey, if the gossip about me kissing in front of everyone reaches Jodi or Caroline, I'm ruined.$s#$b#You need to learn to control yourself!$l#$b#My face is burning up...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.10": "E-everyone's watching us, how embarrassing!$s#$b#How am I supposed to act normal in here with you like this?$l#$b#I'm all red right now...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.11": "Ugh, @! I take my image very seriously, and you're ruining it!$a#$b#Everyone's laughing or staring at us now.$s#$b#Let go of me, I don't want them to see me all flushed like this.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.12": "@, seriously, I love this but...$l#$b#People are just a few steps away from us.$s#$b#Please unstick yourself from me, I'm nearly melting here!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Haley.13": "Ugh, @!$s#$b#You're gonna wrinkle my new outfit like this!$s#$b#We're in a place full of people, everyone's watching... let go of me before my makeup melts from the heat...$l",

