  "OutdoorKisses.Leah.4": "I-if you keep doing this, I swear I'll run and hide deep in the Forest!$l#$b#How embarrassing...$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Leah.5": "At this rate I'm gonna have to camouflage myself in the town's bushes just to escape this embarrassing exposure!$l#$b#You're impossible, @...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Leah.6": "W-wow... my hands are even shaking from all this shyness!$l#$b#How am I supposed to carve wood later if you leave me in this state in front of the whole town?$l",
