  "IndoorKisses.Leah.1": "Oh, @... I love your affection, but we're in a place full of people.$l#$b#I feel like I'm at an art exhibit where I'm the main piece on display!$s#$b#Please, let's be a little more discreet...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.2": "Hey, take it easy... you're making me embarrassed.$l#$b#I much prefer the quiet of home for moments like this, away from so many curious eyes.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.3": "(Whispering) @, I beg you to stop for a moment! People are watching us.$l#$b#I'm not as outgoing as I seem, and this sudden attention makes me flustered.$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.4": "I-I understand you're happy, but everything draws attention in here.$s#$b#Even our kisses!$l#$b#Let's save this affection for when we're walking alone through the forest.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.5": "@, do you realize almost everyone stopped talking just to look at us?#$b#I don't even know where to hide my face right now.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.6": "Goodness... I feel my heart beating so hard that anyone here could hear it.$l#$b#Y-you don't need to kiss me this much in front of so many people!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.7": "W-wait, @... let's take it easy.$l#$b#I feel like we're the main attraction of this place!$s#$b#I'm turning completely red...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.8": "The air in here was already heavy, but now I feel the temperature rising drastically!$s#$b#...Or maybe it's just my face burning up.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.9": "(Whispering) If I had a canvas and a brush in hand right now, I'd cover my face with it!$l#$b#You're drawing a lot of stares to us.$s#$b#Please, hold back a little.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.10": "@, you're making it so nobody in here can take their eyes off us...$s#$b#I can barely form a sentence with you kissing me like this! I'm dying of embarrassment...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.11": "You're impossible! I try to stay composed, and you ruin it all with a single kiss.$l#$b#The people around us are giving us little smiles.#$b#Hide my face, please!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Leah.12": "It's very sweet of you to show so much affection, but look how many people are around us!$l#$b#I feel like an open book being read by everyone here, and it makes me incredibly vulnerable.$s",
