  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.3": "H-hey! I haven't built a robot yet to defend myself from public kiss attacks.$l#$b#You're making my brain short-circuit!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.4": "Oh my god, @! Do you want to overheat my vital systems?$l#$b#I can't process this much affectionate information at once with everyone watching!$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.5": "My body temperature rose about three degrees in a matter of seconds.$l#$b#Save some of this enthusiasm for when we're alone somewhere more secluded.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.6": "I actually like your displays of affection, but this is becoming a statistical anomaly!$s#$b#Can you let go of me a little before the whole town comes to catalog what's happening?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.7": "W-wait! I need to calibrate my emotions, you caught me completely off guard.$l#$b#I'm a scientist, @, I don't know how to handle this much affection in public!$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.8": "My heartbeat is so loud it's completely distorting my ability to think.$s#$b#You leave me completely out of tune, @...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.9": "I'm going to have to invent a clinginess-repelling force field if you keep acting like this in public!$s#$b#...Save all this affection for when we go stargazing in peace, okay?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.10": "If you keep kissing me like this, I-I'm gonna use my invisibility invention!$l#$b#Oh, right, I still haven't finished the prototype... so just let go of me, please!$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.11": "Oh my god, @! My face must be redder than the surface of Mars.$s#$b#Let's get out of here before I evaporate from embarrassment.$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.12": "My focus should be on astronomy, not calculating the probability of the whole town gossiping about us!$s#$b#You take me completely off my axis... but not here!$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Maru.13": "S-seriously, if we keep this up, I'm gonna need a portable heat sink just for myself.$s#$b#I love you, but my daily limit for public social interactions has already overflowed!$s",

  "IndoorKisses.Maru.1": "My hands are even shaking a little.$s#$b#You take my breath away when you do this, and with people around it's even worse.$l#$b#Just give me a second, okay?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.2": "W-wait! I completely lost my train of thought.$l#$b#Everyone's too close, and I don't know how to fake being natural that well.$s#$b#Let go of me a little, please...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.3": "(Whispering) @, i-if my dad sees this, he'll ask me embarrassing questions for the whole week.$s#$b#Save all this affection for later, when we have more privacy...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.4": "M-my temperature rose so much I bet you could measure it with more than one thermometer!$s#$b#Seriously, people are staring at us...$s#$b#Let's act natural before I melt from embarrassment.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.5": "H-hey... I love how ${affectionate^affectionate}$ you are, but an enclosed space with people nearby isn't exactly a combination that puts me at ease.$s#$b#I'm dying of embarrassment...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.6": "...@! I feel like we've become the center of gravity of this place, everyone's eyes are orbiting around us!$l#$b#I-I can't handle this much sudden attention.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.7": "Stop it, please!$s#$b#The probability of someone gossiping about us to my mom in the next few hours just rose to almost one hundred percent!$s#$b#I wish I could bury my head in a hole right now.$s",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.8": "I-I'm terrible at handling situations I can't predict or calculate... and you hugging me in front of everyone was definitely not in today's forecast!$l#$b#Give me a little space, come on.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.9": "@, if Harvey sees me this red, he's gonna think something happened to me or that I caught a virus.$s#$b#Stop it...$s#$b#We're drawing way too much attention.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.10": "(Whispering) @, y-you can't just keep kissing me like this in front of everyone...$l#$b#I'm happy about your affection, but I'm also dying of embarrassment.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.11": "@, control yourself! I'd rather be dealing with a workbench full of tiny parts than have everyone watching us right now.$s#$b#It's way too cramped in here for this kind of affection.#$b#I'm melting from embarrassment...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.12": "Wow, @... you caught me completely off guard.$l#$b#I like your affection, truly, but there are too many people watching in here.$s#$b#Now my face is burning up...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Maru.13": "Hey, take it easy! You like testing my limits in public, don't you?$s#$b#Being kissed in an enclosed space with all these eyes fixed on us makes me want to run away from here$l",

  //PENNY

  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.1": "Oh my god... @, please! We're in a public place!$s#$b#My face must look like a tomato, it's so red...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.2": "What if Jas and Vincent see us?! What kind of example would I be setting?$l#$b#P-please, can we stop this? Everyone's watching!$s",
