  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.4": "I... I wish I had a really thick book right now to hide my face.$l#$b#You're making me die of embarrassment, @.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.5": "Oh, @... I love being close to you, but out here?$s#$b#I feel like the whole town stopped their chores just to watch us...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.6": "Y-you're making me so flustered that I'm even forgetting how to conjugate the basic verbs I teach the kids!$l#$b#P-please stop for a bit, would you?$s",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.7": "I can't handle this much attention...$l#$b#P-please, can we go somewhere quieter, under a tree, far away from everyone?$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.8": "M-my god... My legs are even wobbly.$l#$b#If you keep kissing me nonstop like this, I swear I'll faint from embarrassment right here.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.9": "D-don't you think this is a little... inappropriate to do in public?$s#$b#I feel my face burning in a way I didn't even know was possible...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.10": "I swear I'll lock myself in the trailer and not come out for the rest of the day if you don't stop hugging me in the middle of the street!$l#$b#...This is too much exposure for me...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.11": "Oh no... even Mayor Lewis seems to have stopped to look! How embarrassing.$l#$b#@, please, have mercy on me and let go of me a little.$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.12": "I'm very, very shy about this, @... You know that.$s#$b#Save these kisses for when it's just the ${two of us^two of us}$...$l",
  "OutdoorKisses.Penny.13": "R-read a book, watch some birds, do literally anything else...$l#$b#But please, stop kissing me this much in a public place! My heart can't take it!$l",

  "IndoorKisses.Penny.1": "@, wait a moment! Everyone's focused on us!$s#$b#Please, stop this, at least in here.$l#$b#I can barely breathe from embarrassment!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.2": "P-please, contain yourself!$l#$b#If my mom finds out about this, I'll never have peace in my life again!$l#$b#You know how fast gossip spreads around here...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.3": "This place suddenly feels so small...$l#$b#Everyone's watching us and I don't even have anywhere to run, so let's have some manners, okay?$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.4": "W-wait! I need to be a good example for the town's children.$s#$b#And being seen kissing in front of so many people definitely doesn't help much.$s#$b#Save this for later...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.5": "(Whispering) I feel like my body temperature just shot through the roof!$s#$b#Don't leave me this embarrassed in front of everyone in here.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.6": "If I could, I'd disappear right now.$s#$b#People won't stop looking this way, and I don't know what to do with my hands or where to look!$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.7": "You startled me!$l#$b#And the worst part is you startled everyone around us too, they stopped talking just to watch what we were doing.$l#$b#What absolute embarrassment...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.8": "I love peace and quiet, but you turned this place into the center of attention with all these kisses!$s#$b#I wasn't made for this level of exposure.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.9": "Some people are smiling, others are just staring... and I'm about to have a nervous breakdown from all this shyness!$l#$b#I know you love me, but show it somewhere emptier.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.10": "(Whispering) My heart is beating so hard I swear the people next to us can hear it.$l#$b#This room is way too cramped for you to kiss me like this.$s#$b#Let's be more discreet.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.11": "I was going to tell you something important, but with you kissing me in front of everyone I completely forgot!$l#$b#You leave me totally flustered.$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.12": "I-I feel like apologizing to everyone here for our behavior.$s#$b#We can't act like this in public.$s#$b#My face is on fire, @...$l",
  "IndoorKisses.Penny.13": "I swear I'll run out the door if you don't stop this right now.$a#$b#I-I don't have the courage to face anyone after this whole display!$l"
}
